-- Brazil builder MRV sees 'good' Q2 sales, stable leverage -CEO
-- By Asher Levine and Marcela Ayres
-- Thu Jul 10, 2014 03:42PM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, July 10 (Reuters) - MRV Engenharia <MRVE3.SA>, Brazil's largest low-income homebuilder, is unfazed by a potential economic slowdown and optimistic that upcoming changes to the federal government's subsidized housing program will help support growth, co-Chief Executive Officer Eduardo Fischer told Reuters on Thursday.

